<h4 class='help_title'>About Music Knows</h4>

<p>
  Music companies fuck everything up with DRM and Copyright, the one thing left they don't own are our memories.
  <center><h4><big>&ldquo;</big>Music Knows, because there's no DRM in memory.<big>&rdquo;</big></h4></center>
</p>

<div>
  I used to play in a band. I've been a fan of live music for as long as I can remember. Whenever I meet up with friends we talk about gigs we've been to, and bands we'd like to see. Building Music Knows is my attempt at using the web to record these kind of personal memories - the bands and gigs I've been to that I can still remember are memorable because of the friends I went with, as much as the quality of the music.
